    <item>
      <title>Video Games</title>
      <link>/tags/video-games/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Aug 2025 12:25:46 +0100</pubDate>
      <guid>/tags/video-games/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve always loved video games. From LAN parties in the early 2000s to working in the industry, gaming has been a constant thread through my life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;float-right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/tags/video-games/15033503-AA83-407F-B753-B397AD3FCF47_1_102_a.jpeg  &#34;
         alt=&#34;The Shark Dash team in Hanoi&#34; width=&#34;300&#34;/&gt; &lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;15033503-AA83-407F-B753-B397AD3FCF47_1_102_a.jpeg&#34;&gt;Shark Dash Team at Gameloft Hanoi Studio, Oct 2014&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In 2014, I moved to Vietnam and joined Gameloft as a game producer in their Hanoi studio. I managed teams of a variety of sizes and spent many nights coordinating releases. It also got me a
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mobygames.com/person/816528/christian-k-ndig/&#34;&gt;MobyGames&lt;/a&gt; profile.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
